요 ​ ​ ​ ​         콩고물 묻은 인절미 같기도 하고 길다란 엿 같기도 한 가래떡츄러스는 쌀떡으로 만든 간식이라 밀가루보다 더 든든하면서 안심이 되는 먹거리예요 가래떡이 식으면  딱딱해지니까 굳기전에 드셔야해요       ​ ​       아이들이 좋아하는 츄러스를 우리 떡으로 만들어보세요~~ 기름에 풍덩 튀기지 않아도 바삭하고 고소한 맛에 달달함까지   재료준비도 쉽고 만들기도 간편한 가래떡츄러스를 오늘의 간식으로 추천합니다           오픈캐스트74호는 단감요리입니다      notice~~모든 자료에 대한 불펌은 금합니다                      ","images":["http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141119_232/naya399_14163866386262JBrx_JPEG/%B0%A1%B7%A1%B6%B1%C3%F2%B7%AF%BD%BA_%285%29.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141119_168/naya399_14163866393432aQTW_JPEG/%B0%A1%B7%A1%B6%B1%C3%F2%B7%AF%BD%BA_%286%29.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141119_139/naya399_1416386639145Pax8q_JPEG/%B0%A1%B7%A1%B6%B1%C3%F2%B7%AF%BD%BA_%283%29.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141119_43/naya399_1416386639620AFlQR_JPEG/%B0%A1%B7%A1%B6%B1%C3%F2%B7%AF%BD%BA%B8%B8%B5%E9%B1%E2_%281%29.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141119_172/naya399_1416386639883LY1s7_JPEG/%B0%A1%B7%A1%B6%B1%C3%F2%B7%AF%BD%BA%B8%B8%B5%E9%B1%E2_%282%29.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141119_264/naya399_1416386640055Y0jdM_JPEG/%B0%A1%B7%A1%B6%B1%C3%F2%B7%AF%BD%BA%B8%B8%B5%E9%B1%E2_%283%29.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141119_284/naya399_1416386640243wEDSJ_JPEG/%B0%A1%B7%A1%B6%B1%C3%F2%B7%AF%BD%BA%B8%B8%B5%E9%B1%E2_%284%29.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141119_142/naya399_1416386640405HWvXO_JPEG/%B0%A1%B7%A1%B6%B1%C3%F2%B7%AF%BD%BA%B8%B8%B5%E9%B1%E2_%285%29.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141119_7/naya399_1416386640593rJHPm_JPEG/%B0%A1%B7%A1%B6%B1%C3%F2%B7%AF%BD%BA%B8%B8%B5%E9%B1%E2_%286%29.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141119_12/naya399_14163866410256TQL1_JPEG/%B0%A1%B7%A1%B6%B1%C3%F2%B7%AF%BD%BA%B8%B8%B5%E9%B1%E2_%287%29.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141119_292/naya399_1416386641285ML66g_JPEG/%B0%A1%B7%A1%B6%B1%C3%F2%B7%AF%BD%BA%B8%B8%B5%E9%B1%E2_%288%29.JPG?type=","http://mblog